# Shared by the app image (./Dockerfile) and the server image
# (server/Dockerfile) — both build from the repo root. The app image builds the
# source tree itself, so nothing under src/ or public/ may be excluded here;
# keep only build artifacts and local junk out of the context.
**/node_modules
**/dist
.next
out
.git
.github
test-results
playwright-report
storybook-static
*.log
.DS_Store
